---
const cards = [
  {
    title: "Forecasting Cash Flow",
    desc: "We ensure you’re never blindsided by unexpected expenses. With our expertise, your cash inflow and outflow stay predictable, smooth, and transparent.",
  },
  {
    title: "Balancing Receivables & Payables",
    desc: "We design strategies to improve liquidity, strengthen credibility, bridge cash gaps, and help you use your resources wisely.",
  },
  {
    title: "Expenses Tracking",
    desc: "We monitor spending, eliminate unnecessary costs, and help reduce financial strain so you can reinvest savings into growth.",
  },
  {
    title: "Risk & Contingency Planning",
    desc: "We build contingency reserves and risk-mitigation plans so financial uncertainty doesn’t disrupt your business.",
  },
  {
    title: "Tailored Solutions, Not Templates",
    desc: "Every startup and SMB has unique challenges, so our cash flow management plans are fully customized—never one-size-fits-all.",
  },
  
];
---

<div
  class="main-container w-full pt-[80px] pr-[20px] pb-[80px] pl-[20px] lg:pr-[120px] lg:pl-[120px] flex flex-col gap-[32px] justify-start items-start bg-[#106253] relative mx-auto"
>
  <!-- Heading -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1200px] flex justify-start items-center">
    <span
      class="font-['Inter'] text-[24px] sm:text-[28px] md:text-[32px] lg:text-[36px] font-bold leading-[1.2] text-white"
    >
      Why Choose Finkeepers?
    </span>
  </div>
<div class="w-full max-w-[1200px]">
  <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#ffffff] text-left">
     Finkeepers know that startups and SMB's cash flow management can make or break them,
and later is not an option. Hence, here is why you should opt for cashflow management services
for your business:
      </p>
  </div>
  <!-- Cards Container -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1200px] flex flex-col gap-[25px]">
    <!-- Row 1 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-[25px]">
      {
        cards.slice(0, 3).map((card, index) => (
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-[18px] bg-[#0F5448] rounded-[16px] border border-[#0F5448] shadow-[0px 3px 10px 1px #0000001C]  p-[20px] flex-1 
                      transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:z-10 relative"
          >
            <!-- Number in top-left corner -->
            <div class="absolute -top-[20px] -left-[20px] flex w-[48px] h-[48px] justify-center items-center bg-white rounded-full border-2 border-[#106253]"
            style="left: 15px">
              <span class="text-[#106253] font-bold text-[22px]">
                {String(index + 1).padStart(2)}
              </span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-[20px] sm:text-[22px] leading-[28px] mt-4">
              {card.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-white text-[16px] leading-[22px] font-['Inter']" style="letter-spacing: 0.3px;">
              {card.desc}
            </span>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-[25px]" style="margin-top: 10px;">
      {
        cards.slice(3).map((card, index) => (
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-[18px] bg-[#0F5448] rounded-[16px] border border-[#0F5448] shadow-[0px 3px 10px 1px #0000001C]  p-[20px] flex-1 
                      transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:z-10 relative"
          >
             <!-- Number in top-left corner -->
            <div class="absolute -top-[20px] -left-[20px] flex w-[48px] h-[48px] justify-center items-center bg-white rounded-full border-2 border-[#106253]"
            style="left: 15px">
              <span class="text-[#106253] font-bold text-[22px]">
                {String(index + 4).padStart(2)}
              </span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-[20px] sm:text-[22px] leading-[28px] mt-4">
              {card.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-white text-[16px] leading-[22px] font-['Inter']" style="letter-spacing: 0.3px;">
              {card.desc}
            </span>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
